HEADWORD: Longevity
<hw>Lon*gev"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>longaevitas</ets>. See <er>Longevous</er>.]</ety> <def>Long
duration of life; length of life.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The instances of <qex>longevity</qex> are chiefly amongst the
abstemious.</q> <rj><qau>Arbuthnot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Longevous</ent>⟦br⟧
